<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ticonderoga | The Future of Analog</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;500;800&display=swap');

        :root {
            --primary-yellow: #FFB300;
            --bg-color: #0A0A0A;
            --text-light: #F5F5F7;
            --text-muted: #86868B;
            --accent-green: #2E7D32;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 5%;
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--primary-yellow);
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-yellow);
        }

        .btn-buy {
            background: var(--primary-yellow);
            color: var(--bg-color);
            padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-buy:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        header {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 5%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1a1a1a 0%, #0a0a0a 100%);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F5F5F7, #86868B);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 600px;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .hero-pencil {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary-yellow);
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* Specs Section */
        .specs {
            padding: 8rem 5%;
            background: #111;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .card {
            background: #1A1A1A;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary-yellow);
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 300;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        /* Tech Specs Banner */
        .tech-banner {
            background: var(--primary-yellow);
            color: var(--bg-color);
            padding: 4rem 5%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .tech-banner h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .tech-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 4rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .stat h4 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .stat p {
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 5%;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">TICONDEROGA</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#features">Features</a>
            <a href="#specs">Tech Specs</a>
            <a href="#design">Design</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn-buy">Pre-order</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header>
        <div class="hero-pencil">Series #2 HB</div>
        <h1>The Ultimate<br>Analog Input Device.</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Experience zero-latency tactile feedback with our proprietary graphite core technology. No batteries. No software updates. Just pure, unadulterated creation.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-buy" style="font-size: 1.2rem; padding: 1rem 2.5rem;">Upgrade your workflow</a>
    </header>

    <section class="specs" id="features">
        <h2 class="section-title">Disrupting the blank page.</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <span class="icon">⚡</span>
                <h3>Infinite Battery Life</h3>
                <p>Leave the charger behind. The Ticonderoga #2 utilizes ambient kinetic energy (your hand) to deliver 100% uptime. Always on. Always ready.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <span class="icon">🛡️</span>
                <h3>Biometric Deletion</h3>
                <p>Made a mistake? Our patented pink rubber end-cap features localized mechanical scrubbing to permanently delete errors with zero digital footprint.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <span class="icon">🎯</span>
                <h3>Hexagonal Ergonomics</h3>
                <p>Designed with a 6-sided anti-roll chassis. We re-engineered gravity so your device stays exactly where you placed it on the desk.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <span class="icon">🌲</span>
                <h3>Sustainable Casing</h3>
                <p>Encased in premium, responsibly sourced incense-cedar wood. It doesn't just feel good in the hand; it smells like raw productivity.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="tech-banner" id="specs">
        <h2>Unprecedented Specs</h2>
        <p>Built for professionals. Priced for everyone.</p>
        
        <div class="tech-stats">
            <div class="stat">
                <h4>0ms</h4>
                <p>Latency</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <h4>45k</h4>
                <p>Words per charge (sharpen)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <h4>100%</h4>
                <p>Cloud-Free Privacy</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <h4>#2</h4>
                <p>Graphite Hardness</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 Ticonderoga Inc. All rights reserved. "Graphite Core Technology" and "Biometric Deletion" are completely made up for dramatic effect.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
